de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface ResourceModifier

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface ResourceModifier
extends ElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Resource Modifier'. A general definition of a resource modifier. For instance a discrete output resource could appear in 100 and 250 mA output current levels. In this case the modifier is "current level" and the levels are 100 and 250.

    The following features are supported:

    • Levels
    See Also:
    de.oaam.model.oaam.library.LibraryPackage#getResourceModifier()

    • Method Detail

      • getLevels

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<ModifierLevel> getLevels()
        Returns the value of the 'Levels' containment reference list. The list contents are of type ModifierLevel. The definition of levels allowed for this modifier type. This can be restricted for a certain resource type in the modifier definition.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Levels' containment reference list.
